import { Input } from '@mui/material'
import { Form } from 'antd'
import { useState } from 'react'

export default function Body(){
  const [name,setName]= useState('')

  return <>
    <Form>
        <Form.Item
            name={['name']}
            label= "Nome completo"
        >
        </Form.Item>

        <Form.Item
            name={['email']}
            label="email">
        </Form.Item>
        <Form.Item
            name={['phone']}
            label="Telefone"
        >            
        </Form.Item>

    </Form>
  </>

}
